--------------------------------------------------------------------------
Introduction
--------------------------------------------------------------------------

This script plots the station uptimes computed from the output of the 
uptime_csv.sql query found in groups/mango/support/lib/sql. That output
is a CSV file and is feed as input to this program.

The uptime_plot program is installed with the rest of the transport
application and can be run as:

    uv run uptime_plot <inputfile>


